00:11:53,728 --> 00:11:56,098
Attorney lady!

177
00:11:56,098 --> 00:11:58,858
Please save us!

178
00:12:01,338 --> 00:12:03,928
Save us!

179
00:12:13,588 --> 00:12:14,778
So what you're saying is...

180
00:12:14,778 --> 00:12:17,808
You invested in cryptocurrency with the informal savings club's money,

181
00:12:17,808 --> 00:12:21,538
- but you're about to lose all of that money.
