182
00:12:21,538 --> 00:12:26,188
And that informal savings club was formed together with Dr. Woo Jin on the second floor...

183
00:12:26,908 --> 00:12:29,368
and with Kim Jeong Ho.

184
00:12:29,368 --> 00:12:30,378
Yeah...

185
00:12:30,378 --> 00:12:33,698
