198
00:13:11,258 --> 00:13:13,518
So what then?

199
00:13:13,518 --> 00:13:15,788
We invested just a bit more...

200
00:13:15,788 --> 00:13:18,538
So exactly how much of it did you put in?

201
00:13:23,598 --> 00:13:25,598
5 million...?

202
00:13:30,258 --> 00:13:35,118
- 50 million!
- 50 million?

203
00:13:36,208 --> 00:13:38,018
But this...

204
00:13:38,018 --> 00:13:40,368
The landlord must not know about this!

205
00:13:40,368 --> 00:13:44,198
