214
00:14:26,248 --> 00:14:28,498
- and it required a lot of loans.
- Nah...

215
00:14:28,498 --> 00:14:30,838
But it still wouldn't have been cheap.

216
00:14:30,838 --> 00:14:32,388
Hey, Honeybee!

217
00:14:32,388 --> 00:14:34,398
