224
00:14:52,538 --> 00:14:53,938
Speaking of which,

225
00:14:53,938 --> 00:14:58,148
in the beginning, she explained to us how we could check the profits.

226
00:14:58,148 --> 00:15:02,528
Those profits are received in this "coin wallet."

227
00:15:02,528 --> 00:15:05,398
So with regards to how we could turn this into cash,

228
00:15:05,398 --> 00:15:08,268
