229
00:15:08,268 --> 00:15:12,138
I mean, how can someone leave out such an important part?

230
00:15:12,138 --> 00:15:14,008
Yeah.

231
00:15:14,008 --> 00:15:16,488
Such an important part...

232
00:15:18,338 --> 00:15:20,818
Deception by omission.

233
00:15:21,828 --> 00:15:24,638
Deceiving another person by not sharing an important piece of information,

234
00:15:24,638 --> 00:15:27,578
by not sharing an important piece of information,

235
00:15:27,578 --> 00:15:30,198
can also be considered fraud.

236
00:15:30,198 --> 00:15:33,068
How long have you known this?

237
00:15:33,818 --> 00:15:35,198
Tell me.

238
00:15:35,198 --> 00:15:38,198
Did you know from the start? Did you?

239
00:15:43,328 --> 00:15:48,908
But... this is not the end of the story.

240
00:15:48,908 --> 00:15:50,698
What! There's more?

241
00:15:50,698 --> 00:15:52,198
So...

242
00:15:57,158 --> 00:15:59,668
It's so annoying!

